{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "“血鑽”的歌聲", "storyInfo": "拍攝地塊在源石風暴中遭到破壞，蒂比震驚於真兇竟是好友的事實，決意拯救地塊。與此同時，盧西恩再次找到已經陷入癲狂的莫伊拉。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_wind", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind_howling", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sn"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g8_mobileplotstreet_ruined", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$jealous_intro", "key": "$jealous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是*藍卡塢片場術語*格蕾塔的拍攝計劃？！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都貼在源石風暴的臉上了！明顯是想讓我們送死啊！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不……一定是兇手幹的！你沒聽到之前的爆炸聲嗎？", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地塊的駕駛室被人為炸毀了……我們現在根本沒辦法改變地塊的移動速度和航向……", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在地塊接觸的還只是天災的最外圍，等我們真的撞向它的正中心之後……", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "整個地塊可能連一塊完整的磚塊都不剩吧……嗚嗚嗚……", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了別說了！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底是誰？連續死了這麼多人還不夠，現在還想帶走所有人的命嗎？！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兇、兇手是道具組的莫伊拉……", "name": "無線電中的聲音"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？誰在說話？", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#4$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說！地塊上發生的三起兇殺案，兇手就是莫伊拉！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#4$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉……天……就是那個不起眼的小札拉克？", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士親眼所見！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是盧西恩先生在場，我們的製片人也遇害了！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那個混蛋在哪裡？我要去找她！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你自己的命都快沒了，找一個喪心病狂的殺人犯理論還有什麼用！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道她不用付出一點代價嗎？如果有不知情的劇組成員又遇害該怎麼辦！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你都能想到的問題，難道我想不到嗎？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了保命，我已經把無線電對講機調成廣播模式，真相現在應該已經傳到所有人的耳朵裡了。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兇手絕不敢輕舉妄動。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得保住自己這條值錢的命……等回到藍卡塢主城區，我就能用這幾天收集到的重磅八卦在汐斯塔買套度假別墅了——", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟了！地塊又往源石風暴的方向偏移了！", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，陸行艇！那些陸行艇能救我們！", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……沒了。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說什麼？", "name": "憤怒的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去緊急逃生艙看過了，所有的陸行艇都已經被源石風暴破壞了……沒有一架是好的……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們已經無路可逃了……", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……與其死在風暴裡，我還不如從地塊上跳下去……我……", "name": "害怕的工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說傻話！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走，哪裡都比拍攝區安全，先到地下動力層躲一下！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "r"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "r", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sn", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g12_dressingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldtvelectricity", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "fi"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "fi", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "fi", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_filmprojection"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐怖片的場景設計確實有很多值得參考的地方……謝謝你，蒂比。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小意思！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大致的呈現效果我需要先回去做一個樣本，等到斯蒂芬導演修改完劇本，我們再慢慢敲定細節。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應過您，一定會設計出讓“杜邦夫人”留名影史的落幕場景！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，合作愉快。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉，已經這麼晚了嗎？不知道莫麗有沒有找到離開地塊的方法——）", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 4.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎、怎麼回事？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不太對勁。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#5$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，米蘭妮女士，無線電有聲音……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……天災……（雜音）……中控駕駛室……毀……", "name": "無線電中的聲音"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "訊號怎麼這麼差？這個聲音好像是阿布納的攝影助理？他又在亂傳什麼八卦——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中控駕駛室……炸毀了……", "name": "無線電中的聲音"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地塊……正衝向天災……", "name": "無線電中的聲音"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……兇手……都是莫伊拉……", "name": "無線電中的聲音"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比緊握住無線電對講機，用力地轉動音量鍵，然而對講機裡只剩一片死寂……"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一定是自己聽錯了，她想。"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，米蘭妮女士為什麼要這樣憂鬱地看著自己？"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不可能……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比……沒有人會在這個節骨眼開玩笑……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是……莫麗根本沒有作案的時間啊？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉、邁克爾、瑪麗昂遇害的晚上，她一直都跟我待在一起看電影，根本沒機會——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真的沒機會嗎？"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比在心中質問自己。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每次看電影莫麗都會陪自己整個晚上，寸步不離嗎？"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為我們每次都是好幾部恐怖片一起看，所以她偶爾會在換光碟的時候，稍微離開一陣子……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候是說格蕾塔女士有事找她，有時候說東西還放在拍攝現場，要回去拿……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮女士，你知道的，她剛當上道具組長，壓力很大，很認真地對待自己的工作……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對不對，這最多只能說她具備犯案的條件，並不能直接證明她就是兇手啊……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動機呢？她為什麼要殺這些與她毫不相關的人？為什麼我什麼事情都不知道？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，或許，你只是沒那麼瞭解自己的朋友……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i12", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4, "y": 0.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們把注意力放在電影啦……莫麗，你不要老是分心！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，劇組最近發生的事情太多了，我……我有點緊張……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我在你身邊啊！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管我是什麼身分，在這個劇組裡，我都是你最好最好的朋友！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g12_dressingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又或許，莫麗她，從來都沒把我當成，朋友……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她只是想，利用我……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黎博利女孩把頭垂得很低。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她再也說不出一句話。"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "50,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮抱住了眼前小小的黎博利。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾個小時前還在安慰她的女孩，現在靠在自己的肩頭哭泣。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮輕撫著女孩的後背，她沒有再追問什麼，也沒有幫對方總結所謂成長的代價，只是抱著她……"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於現在，蒂比，跟我離開這裡吧。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建築內複雜的結構太多，如果地塊繼續靠近天災中心，這裡會變得很危險。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要快點去地下避難，雖然地塊的航向不變的話，這麼做也無濟於事……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#4$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "地下……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "越過米蘭妮的肩頭，蒂比看到了她們剛剛從恐怖片中整理出的資料。"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“地下”這個關鍵詞在她的腦海中盤旋。"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#2$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，我明白了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼了？這麼快就恢復情緒了？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#3$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我是想到改變地塊航向的辦法了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個劇組曾經為了省掉地塊租金，偷偷潛入藍卡塢另一個地塊的地下結構拍攝實景，完成了一部很酷的恐怖片……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我最近才又看過一遍。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個地塊和我們腳下的這個地塊，是藍卡塢出產的同一批拍攝用地塊……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是說，它們的規格和框架是差不多的。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我沒有猜錯……動力層的深處應該有一個備用的機械控制室。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……有幾成把握？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話……完全沒有把握。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#3$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我必須去做。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有些事情，胡思亂想是得不到答案的。只有等到危機解決之後……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才能去找她問清楚。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（溫柔的歌聲♪）", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（清亮的口哨♪）", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，你來了？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_rglk1normal1_intro", "key": "$m_bat_rglk1normal1_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是姐姐她最喜歡的歌，拍戲的空檔，她經常望著天空哼著這首歌。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為，你已經清醒了。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確實已經清醒了啊。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了你，讓我看到了被自己視而不見的真相……它們真是，太殘忍了啊。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你現在，是在做什麼？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轟隆隆的聲響自腳下傳來，這座藍卡塢地塊正朝著天災加速狂奔，人們都在驚慌避難，不會再有工作人員試圖來到道具間……"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而就在此時，道具師做起了她的本職工作。"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在道具間來回穿梭，擺布著一個又一個道具人偶，為它們穿上衣服，為它們糾正姿勢……專注而認真。"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就在剛剛，我終於想起自己是怎麼認識勞拉的了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "容我猜測……你遇見了一個人。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，一位很溫柔的菲林。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cavewaterdrop", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "ca"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "ca", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "cg_floatingleaves", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 60.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那天天氣很差，我在長椅上坐了很久，我的臉上有水，應該是雨滴，或者眼淚……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明是那個負責人的疏忽導致了事故，但最後，賠光了錢還被趕出劇組的，是我。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在藍卡塢沒認識多少人，這樣的事情已經經歷過很多次了。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是從家鄉逃出來的，爸爸媽媽死後，我已經無處可去，只剩下……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後那個人在旁邊坐了下來，我們全程沒有說一句話，他只是溫柔地等我平復下來……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他離開之後，我發現自己的膝蓋上多了一個錄影帶。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ca", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g6_proproom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人在我看不見任何光亮的時候，將勞拉帶進了我的人生。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉成為了我的姐姐，她守護著我、鼓勵著我，讓我一點點重新振作起來……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候，勞拉早已死去。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉的出身、經歷甚至長相都與你相似，那個人為你帶來了身處絕境所必需的動力……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也為你帶來了憤怒、困惑、刻骨的仇恨和復仇的渴望……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，那是另一種絕境。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#6$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，你的眼神中閃過了一絲哀傷……不對，是憐憫？也不對……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更像是一種了然於心，一種感同身受。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你的身上，發生過類似的事情嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你認識那個人？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他擅長將一段本不存在的喜怒嫁接進你的人生，就像一個恣意妄為的導演，蠻橫地在一個他認為乏味的故事裡融入……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，用我新學會的電影術語來說——“即興創作”。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他將你拉出絕境，又引導你踏進另一種絕境，由此來激發所謂戲劇的美。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……他是我的舊識，我的老師，我所有痛苦的根源，一個本應早已死去的幽靈。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#8$1"}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到你，找到他……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#8$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為此而來。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#8$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#14$2"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉，很遺憾否定了你的一切。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#10$2"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是這樣的，盧西恩先生。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#7$2"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉擺正了最後一個人偶，回到了道具間的正中央。"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她朝盧西恩施了一個禮，輕輕扣了扣指尖。"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩在一瞬間覺察到了異樣，抬眼望去，所有的人偶都“活”了過來——"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4, "y": 0.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不認為你否定了我什麼。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我人生最絕望的時候，勞拉出現在我的身邊，陪伴我度過了漫長時光……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勞拉就是我的姐姐，我就是勞拉的妹妹。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不後悔為她報仇，我不後悔背負這些罪孽。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我會成為這片大地上最後一個記得她的人。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我哭、我笑、我憤怒、我疑惑、我憎恨、我悲哀、我懷念……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我因此擁有了，我本無法擁有的一切強烈體會——", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我活著。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_puppetmove_horror", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "pu"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "pu", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "62_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人偶們動了起來。"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩認出了人偶的原型……那是死去的道爾頓、謝莉、邁克爾和瑪麗昂，以及，她自己。"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉伸出手臂，與經過自己身邊的人偶逐一相挽，錯身。"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有音樂配合，地面也在晃動，但小小的札拉克道具師此刻仿若成為了世間最忘情的舞者，她與萬千個人相擁……"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "詭異而優雅。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "pu", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實我應該感謝你，盧西恩先生，你讓我意識到……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“莫伊拉”已經什麼都不剩的時候……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得自己變成了一面鏡子，我可以是——", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "任何人！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清醒。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因絕望而生的滿足，只是毒藥。", "name": "盧西恩"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的人生再也沒有哪一刻比現在更清醒了，盧西恩先生。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也要，成為我的舞伴嗎？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……像它們一樣。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫伊拉話音落下的瞬間，她的舞伴們撲向了盧西恩——"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "pu", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_puppetrun_horror", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 6.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 415, "